{"tid":1331502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豬神提堂","createTime":"2019-07-19T03:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T03:51:54.000Z","uid":36248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e039ea93e93c838a8776e616a933b30cf468f910","tid":1331502,"uid":36248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:12:39.000Z","msg":"【九龍灣連儂牆襲擊案】<br />\n<br />\n一名46歲男子本月11日於九龍灣一幅市民自製的「連儂牆」前，襲擊兩名男子，涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，今日於觀塘裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n任職的士司機的被告黃堅海出庭，控方表示，被告本月11日於九龍灣東九龍文化中心地盤外，因為張貼紙張的問題爭執，被告在警方警誡下，承認襲擊兩名男子，亦有影片佐證，被告並不認識兩名事主。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官溫紹明要求被告以5000元現金繼續保釋，並於逢星期一、三、五到警署報到，案件押後至8月30日提訊，等待控方向律政司徵詢控罪意見。"},{"pid":"9b47e4f9fd4f05f863531959b31b3266b91e7280","tid":1331502,"uid":36248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18bcade5285997345a2049e6572231b9d9b0ac1","tid":1331502,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:51:54.000Z","msg":"幾時告埋呢班人?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tIn4OMx-UdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtIn4OMx-UdA&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=9e8dd362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tIn4OMx-UdA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[有片有download Link]蘆葦蔥暗地表示藍白衫克警係暴徒<br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1326547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1326547</a>"}]}